headline: 'Every Game Company' is Doing it? 'Arc Raiders' AI Scandal Explodes, Big Name CEO Suggests Hidden Truth
summary: One should assume "every game company" is using AI, Nexon Co. Ltd. CEO Junghun Lee says. Nexon CEO Defends Widespread AI Adoption in Gaming Under fire for its use of artificial intelligence, Nexon's hit “Arc Raiders” game has ignited fierce debate over the ethical limits of AI in gaming.
